# Steps taken when triaging an alert

 Prioritise the alert and select first
 Assign you name to the alert
 Move the alert to "In progress"
 Read the alert name and description
 Take note of alert fields like IP, User, Host
 Open the SIEM Tool (Splunk or Microsoft Sentinel)
 Investigate and make your final verdict
 Escalate to higher levels if neccessary
 Add your comment
 Move the alert to "closed"
